Overview Run this scenario to collect some training data. Those data will later be used to train a classifier for online use. When you start this scenario, just wait 40 seconds before it starts the instruction sequence. You will then be presented right arrows to let you imagine right hand movements. There will be 30 arrows. If no arrow appears, just relax. note: the recorded files go to the folder where the scenario xml is located (${Player_ScenarioDirectory}/).
